vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for (1) an ordinance granting an MF-2(A) Multifamily District; and (2) a resolution accepting deed restrictions on property zoned an IR Industrial Research District, on the southeast line of Kimsey Drive, north of Orion Place
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval
